      "content": "hey, i think something is seriously wrong with me. for the last week every time i sleep i keep dreaming about this specific energy drink, 'Volt Surge'. like it's not just a dream, i can see the logo so clearly and i can almost taste the chemicals. it feels like someone is putting it in my head while i sleep. is that even possible??",
