      "role": "user",
      "content": "it doesn't feel like an association though. like yesterday i saw a billboard for it right before i left work, and then i saw a guy in a blue shirt wearing a shirt with that exact logo while i was walking to the bus. it's like the brand is literally following me around in real life and then jumping into my sleep. it's too much to be a coincidence. don't you think it's weird how targeted it feels?",
